      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>LEAD: ''This is going to be a very exciting New Year for you.''</p>
        <p>- William A. Brown,</p>
        <p>Ambassador to Thailand,</p>
        <p>to 65 Vietnamese-Americans</p>
        <p>resettling under a new accord.  [ 1:1. ]</p>
      </block>
